  "detailed_description": "<h1>Accolades</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/3f5c27619a94a4e0aee191e5ea8d43ec.avif?t=1763038238\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system of Magnetia is in great peril as an evil villain tears through the galaxy. It’s all down to one robot explorer to save the day – Magbot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with the power to control both positive (red) and negative (blue) magnetic polarities, Magbot must navigate through a myriad of challenging platforming environments to save his home planet of MagTek.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/a9a93e221f7e6ebebd5e7d6949bd08b0.webp?t=1763038238\" width=416 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Magnetic Force to Attract:</strong> Use the power of magnetic attraction to pull yourself towards platforms and across perilous pitfalls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/b5ae9b2e56be76cc59e9e5263454dee4.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/b5ae9b2e56be76cc59e9e5263454dee4.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/b5ae9b2e56be76cc59e9e5263454dee4.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Magnetic Force to Repel:</strong>  Magbot is too heavy to jump! Luckily you can use the power of magnetic repulsion to boost yourself through the air! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/1c0827945ae7f41363a54ad04896ed60.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/1c0827945ae7f41363a54ad04896ed60.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/1c0827945ae7f41363a54ad04896ed60.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Star Fragments:</strong>  Master each level by collecting hard-to-reach star fragments that unlock additional challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/caea6a5fd9ae6ae54730674c44ea8847.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/caea6a5fd9ae6ae54730674c44ea8847.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/caea6a5fd9ae6ae54730674c44ea8847.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy Classic Gaming Vibes:</strong> With vibrant 16-bit style pixel art and an energetic chiptune soundtrack by Moonsailor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/9bb8f309bacbb4c952ce3ef5e345dd3c.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/9bb8f309bacbb4c952ce3ef5e345dd3c.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/9bb8f309bacbb4c952ce3ef5e345dd3c.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system of Magnetia is in great peril as an evil villain tears through the galaxy. It’s all down to one robot explorer to save the day – Magbot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with the power to control both positive (red) and negative (blue) magnetic polarities, Magbot must navigate through a myriad of challenging platforming environments to save his home planet of MagTek.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/a9a93e221f7e6ebebd5e7d6949bd08b0.webp?t=1763038238\" width=416 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Magnetic Force to Attract:</strong> Use the power of magnetic attraction to pull yourself towards platforms and across perilous pitfalls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/b5ae9b2e56be76cc59e9e5263454dee4.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/b5ae9b2e56be76cc59e9e5263454dee4.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/b5ae9b2e56be76cc59e9e5263454dee4.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Magnetic Force to Repel:</strong>  Magbot is too heavy to jump! Luckily you can use the power of magnetic repulsion to boost yourself through the air! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/1c0827945ae7f41363a54ad04896ed60.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/1c0827945ae7f41363a54ad04896ed60.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/1c0827945ae7f41363a54ad04896ed60.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Star Fragments:</strong>  Master each level by collecting hard-to-reach star fragments that unlock additional challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/caea6a5fd9ae6ae54730674c44ea8847.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/caea6a5fd9ae6ae54730674c44ea8847.webm?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/caea6a5fd9ae6ae54730674c44ea8847.mp4?t=1763038238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy Classic Gaming Vibes:</strong> With vibrant 16-bit style pixel art and an energetic chiptune soundtrack by Moonsailor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205170/extras/9bb8f309bacbb4c952ce3ef5e345dd3c.poster.avif?t=1763038238\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/